{"tid":1686013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hong Kong Be Water Act!!!!","createTime":"2019-11-01T01:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T06:34:28.000Z","uid":79599,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3280789a9729e98d877be0a05319e3350a3b1319","tid":1686013,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"曾在港與香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒會面的美國共和黨籍參議員霍利（Josh Hawley），周四（10月31日）提出一條名為《Hong Kong Be Water Act》的法案，內容旨在制裁打壓香港人言論、結社、集會、遊行及示威自由的香港和中國官員以及國企，凍結他們的資產。<br />\n該法案引用美國的《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法(Global Magnitsky Human Rights Accountability Act)》及《國際緊急經濟權力法(International Emergency Economic Powers Act)》制訂，其中在2012年通過的《馬格尼茨基法》，容許美國凍結任何侵犯人權的非美國公民的資產。霍利早前曾來港觀察香港反修例示威的情況，之後與另一共和黨參議員斯科特（Rick Scott）草擬上述法案。<br />\n法案指美國國會認為中國政府刻意違反《中英聯合聲明》和《基本法》，侵食港人的民主自由；又批評中共以經濟手段，威逼多家航空公司以及多個國際知名品牌，對其對付香港示威者的手法噤聲。<br />\n霍利受訪時表示，香港形勢嚴峻，香港人正向美國和世界各地愛好自由的人士尋求支持和力量，因此是時候向香港發出訊息表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n幫手推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n念念不忘，必有迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource： <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191101/mobile/bkn-20191101011035058-1101_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191101%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191101011035058-1101_00822_001.html&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c2101563\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191101/mobile/bkn-20191101011035058-1101_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n官方網頁<a href=\"https://www.hawley.senate.gov/senator-hawley-leads-legislation-combat-beijings-suppression-hongkongers-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawley.senate.gov%2Fsenator-hawley-leads-legislation-combat-beijings-suppression-hongkongers-rights&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b1966f73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hawley.senate.gov/senator-hawley-leads-legislation-combat-beijings-suppression-hongkongers-rights</a><br />\n<br />\ntwitter傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1189928584963592192?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1189928584963592192%3Fs%3D19&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=5603451f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1189928584963592192%3Fs%3D19&h=dac449be\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1189928584963592192?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"1b5266f5354bd7ae130675dfb56852541f4f492d","tid":1686013,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e6c86ba65155b492831fed2be198e502e4d4df0","tid":1686013,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"c985e9e0a9be0e032c96192a30a5bfdf5b8db3d6","tid":1686013,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"f70cab189b18a08f7acce3c9bd0fdf56b6f18097","tid":1686013,"uid":48885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:31:24.000Z","msg":"甴近平表示支持"},{"pid":"3e41f9000ff000ae92c0821931d9cf3cb4064d05","tid":1686013,"uid":327316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"過左HKHRDA先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33690d0921f3c9d6499dab04ca1c23886e4e3808","tid":1686013,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:35:22.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"549b0657bfc71fa20de74c7a7b8cfa27457f7ea8","tid":1686013,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e41f9000ff00